					<div class="panel full" style="float: right; width: 260px; background: #D95D3E; margin: 20px 10px 10px; padding: 15px;">
						<h3 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0 0 15px; padding: 0;">RIW 2015 в цифрах:</h3>
						<p style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: normal; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;"><b style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">2</b> выставки</p>
